<typeStatus id="3C468876BC4FFFDD5046BADDFE23FC64" box="[312,414,982,1008]" pageId="9" pageNumber="32">syntypes</typeStatus>
. One of the two females was labelled by Moure as 
<typeStatus id="3C468876BC4FFFDD52A1BADEFBF4FC7B" box="[991,1097,981,1007]" pageId="9" pageNumber="32">lectotype</typeStatus>
, but that specimen is in worse condition than the other. The female in better condition is here designated the 
<typeStatus id="3C468876BC4FFFDD5288BAF2FBE0FB87" box="[1014,1117,1017,1043]" pageId="9" pageNumber="32">lectotype</typeStatus>
and it has the following data label: [circular label with red margin] 
<typeStatus id="3C468876BC4FFFDD5341BD16FD1AFBA3" box="[575,679,1053,1079]" pageId="9" pageNumber="32">Holotype</typeStatus>
[printed]\ Cay. [handwritten]\ Bres. [handwritten]\ 
